title: Masterpiece DJ Mixes Vol 1-6 [MP3 V0] [Techno, Jazz, Funk, D&amp
description:
Six triple-disc mixes by Ministry of Sound that put emphasis on the creator's influences and fit a theme unique to each artist.

1. Francois K
Style: Downtempo, Techno, House, Tribal, Electro, Tribal House, Future Jazz, Deep House,  Tech House, Ambient, Progressive House, Acid, Dub Techno, Synth-pop, Minimal

Disc 1: Napoli (Techno)
Disc 2: Manchester (Electro)
Disc 3: Tokyo (Deep House)

2. Jazzie B (Soul II Soul)
Style: House, Breaks, Soul, Disco, UK Garage, Deep House, Hip Hop, Garage House, Funk

Disc 1: Pre Africa Centre (Disco)
Disc 2: Africa Centre / Rare Groove (Funk/Soul)
Disc 3: Africa Centre / Fridge (Eclectic)

3. Fabio & Grooverider
Style: Soul-Jazz, House, Disco, Techno, Tech House, Breakbeat, Drum n Bass, Jazz-Funk, Acid House

Disc 1: Fabio Mix (Soul)
Disc 2: Grooverider Mix (House)
Disc 3: Fabio & Grooverider Mix - The Years 1991-2005 (Drum & Bass)

4. Gilles Peterson
Style: House, Latin Jazz, Jazz-Funk, Future Jazz, Jazzdance, Techno, Deep House, Electro, Bass, Breaks

Disc 1: Dusk (Eclectic)
Disc 2: Dawn (Eclectic)
Disc 3: Twilight (Eclectic)

5. Andrew Weatherall
Style: Leftfield, Alternative Rock, Indie Rock, House, Dub, Electro, Downtempo

Disc 1: Eleven O'Clock Drop (Goth, Electro)
Disc 2: Twelve O'Clock Drop (Disco, Electro)
Disc 3: One O'Clock Drop (Techno, Electro)

6. Carl Craig
Style: Techno, Soul, Dub, Downtempo, Experimental

Disc 1: Aspiration (Techno)
Disc 2: Inspiration (Eclectic)
Disc 3: Meditation (Original material)
